:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban\/#Hai_doi\" >Hai \u0111\u00f4i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban\/#Doi\" >\u0110\u00f4i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban\/#Bai_cao\" >B\u00e0i cao<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban\/#Ket_luan\" >K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong>B\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u01a1i Poker v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban\/\">th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i Poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/a>? C\u00e1c kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m bao g\u1ed3m l\u00e1 b\u00e0i n\u00e0o m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n hay l\u00e1 n\u00e0o y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 c\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm r\u00f5. Qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau \u0111\u00e2y, <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\">Nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i SV368<\/a> s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p cho anh em th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 c\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i trong Poker t\u1eeb cao \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea5p. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap bet th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n khi tham gia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u00e0i.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"So_luoc_thong_tin_ve_game_va_thu_tu_bai_Poker_co_ban\"><\/span><b>S\u01a1 l\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 game v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i Poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t v\u00e1n b\u00e0i Poker bao g\u1ed3m 5 l\u00e1 b\u00e0i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t ho\u1eb7c kh\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t. Trong v\u00e1n b\u00e0i, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd gi\u1eef 2 l\u00e1 b\u00e0i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ch\u00fang v\u1edbi 5 l\u00e1 b\u00e0i chung tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh tay b\u00e0i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u1edf 2 l\u00e1 b\u00e0i tr\u00ean tay m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 4 ho\u1eb7c c\u1ea3 5 l\u00e1 b\u00e0i chung \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng tay b\u00e0i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ec3 th\u1eafng m\u1ed9t v\u00e1n Poker, anh em c\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf b\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu tay b\u00e0i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t khi l\u1eadt b\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 <\/span><b>th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i Poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. Khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c tay b\u00e0i Poker theo th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00f4 t\u1ea3. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong b\u00e0i Poker, ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00e1c nhau v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb nh\u01b0 nhau.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3741\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3741\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3741 size-full\" title=\"th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-1.jpg\" alt=\"S\u01a1 l\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 game v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i Poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n\" width=\"800\" height=\"451\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-1.jpg?v=1735810744 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-1-300x169.jpg?v=1735810744 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-1-768x433.jpg?v=1735810744 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3741\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u01a1 l\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 game v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i Poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chi_tiet_thu_tu_bai_Poker_co_ban_tu_lon_nhat_cho_den_be\"><\/span><b>Chi ti\u1ebft th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i Poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n t\u1eeb l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e9<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 c\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i trong Poker s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh em \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i b\u00e0i trong Poker t\u1eeb cao nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm r\u00f5:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sanh_rong\"><\/span><b>S\u1ea3nh r\u1ed3ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1ea3nh r\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 tay b\u00e0i hi\u1ebfm nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00e2n c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a game Poker. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3nh s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i g\u1ed3m 10, J, Q, K, A c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu tay b\u00e0i n\u00e0y th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u1ed1t v\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3743\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3743\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3743 size-full\" title=\"th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-2.jpg\" alt=\"Chi ti\u1ebft th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i Poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n t\u1eeb l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e9\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-2.jpg?v=1735810745 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-2-300x225.jpg?v=1735810745 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-2-768x576.jpg?v=1735810745 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3743\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Chi ti\u1ebft th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i Poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n t\u1eeb l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e9<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Thung_pha_sanh\"><\/span><b>Th\u00f9ng ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3nh<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u00f9ng ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ee9ng ngay sau S\u1ea3nh r\u1ed3ng trong b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng <\/span><b>th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i Poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. S\u1ea3nh n\u00e0y s\u1ebd bao g\u1ed3m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp n\u0103m l\u00e1 b\u00e0i s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t th\u00f9ng ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3nh th\u00ec tay b\u00e0i cao nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng cu\u1ed9c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tu_quy\"><\/span><b>T\u1ee9 qu\u00fd<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ee9 qu\u00fd l\u00e0 tay b\u00e0i g\u1ed3m b\u1ed1n l\u00e1 b\u00e0i gi\u1ed1ng nhau v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00e1 b\u00e0i l\u1ebb. N\u1ebfu t\u1ee9 qu\u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb n\u0103m l\u00e1 b\u00e0i chung th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 l\u00e1 b\u00e0i l\u1ebb cao h\u01a1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n x\u1eed l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cu_lu\"><\/span><b>C\u00f9 l\u0169<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Theo <\/span><b>th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i Poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, c\u00f9 l\u0169 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tay b\u00e0i g\u1ed3m ba l\u00e1 b\u00e0i c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea3 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u00f9 l\u0169 th\u00ec bet th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba l\u00e1 b\u00e0i cao h\u01a1n s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3742\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3742\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3742 size-full\" title=\"th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-3.jpg\" alt=\"T\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 Poker\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-3.jpg?v=1735810744 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-3-300x188.jpg?v=1735810744 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-3-768x480.jpg?v=1735810744 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3742\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 Poker<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Thung\"><\/span><b>Th\u00f9ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u00f9ng l\u00e0 tay b\u00e0i g\u1ed3m n\u0103m l\u00e1 b\u00e0i c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i theo th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1. N\u1ebfu hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u00f9ng th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi l\u00e1 b\u00e0i cao h\u01a1n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng cu\u1ed9c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sanh\"><\/span><b>S\u1ea3nh<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong <\/span><b>th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i Poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, s\u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i tr\u00ean tay v\u00e0 tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 5 l\u00e1 b\u00e0i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu nhi\u1ec1u bet th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ea3nh th\u00ec l\u00e1 b\u00e0i cao nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng cu\u1ed9c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bo_ba\"><\/span><b>B\u1ed9 ba<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng b\u1ed9 ba th\u00ec tay b\u00e0i n\u00e0o cao h\u01a1n s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu c\u1ea3 hai s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ed9 ba gi\u1ed1ng nhau th\u00ec hai l\u00e1 b\u00e0i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3740\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3740\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3740 size-full\" title=\"th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-4.jpg\" alt=\"N\u1eafm r\u00f5 th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i Poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-4.jpg?v=1735810743 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-4-300x200.jpg?v=1735810743 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/thu-tu-bai-poker-co-ban-4-768x513.jpg?v=1735810743 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3740\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">N\u1eafm r\u00f5 th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i Poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Hai_doi\"><\/span><b>Hai \u0111\u00f4i<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hai \u0111\u00f4i l\u00e0 tay b\u00e0i g\u1ed3m hai \u0111\u00f4i kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00e1 b\u00e0i l\u1ebb trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 n\u0103m l\u00e1 trong <\/span><b>th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 b\u00e0i Poker c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. N\u1ebfu nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t bet th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng hai \u0111\u00f4i th\u00ec l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0o cao h\u01a1n s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u00f4i b\u1eb1ng nhau, l\u00e1 b\u00e0i l\u1ebb s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Doi\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u00f4i<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i l\u00e0 tay b\u00e0i g\u1ed3m m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i (2 l\u00e1 b\u00e0i c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1ng) v\u00e0 ba l\u00e1 b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c nhau. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i cao nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c \u0111\u00f4i b\u1eb1ng nhau, ba l\u00e1 b\u00e0i l\u1ebb cao nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bai_cao\"><\/span><b>B\u00e0i cao<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00e0i cao (M\u1eadu th\u1ea7u) l\u00e0 tay b\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i, kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia c\u00f3 b\u00e0i cao th\u00ec l\u00e1 b\u00e0i cao nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 <\/span><b>th\u1e